channel.title: Looking for a server name? Check this out!
channel.description:
Well people have been having troubles with finding good server names lately, so i want you guys to post some ways you can come up with a cool name. Here are afew ive been using
The song your listening to now, or you last listened to, take it and add a Scape or Pkz at the end. It should work 75% of the time.
Take your favourite video game and add a Scape or Pkz to one of the words in it, or the author of the game. ex. Modern Warfare 2, WarfarePkz ModernScape ModernPkz WarfareScape, InfinityPkz InfinityScape WardPkz WardScape InfinityWardPkz InfinityWardScape.
Post your ideas here!
